## 5. Automatic Execution Background Config (Lines 244-291)
```typescript
export async function setAutoBackupEnabled(enabled: boolean): Promise<void> {
    await AsyncStorage.setItem(BACKUP_ENABLED_KEY, enabled.toString());
    if (enabled) scheduleAutoBackup();
    else cancelAutoBackup();
}
```
*   **Logical Flow**: Ties the UI toggle switch to the device scheduler. A background task would be registered with the OS, telling it to wake the phone up at 2 AM, check if the device is plugged in and on Wi-Fi, and automatically fire the backup routine without waking the user.
